00:36:52,653 --> 00:37:00,657
[SPEAKER_02]: And then these are our, as it says, top 10 in terms of apartments on fiscal year, fiscal 26 value.

374
00:37:00,717 --> 00:37:07,180
[SPEAKER_02]: So they typically bear the burden of most of a good portion of the residential levy given their evaluations.

375
00:37:07,620 --> 00:37:13,263
[SPEAKER_02]: So this was just to show in fiscal 26, if we had implemented the full

376
00:37:14,102 --> 00:37:27,247
