00:37:44,544 --> 00:37:49,228
[SPEAKER_02]: So again, same slide, except the different amount that is being added to the levy.

380
00:37:49,488 --> 00:37:56,754
[SPEAKER_02]: And as you can see, the numbers gradually increase for each of the 10 largest apartment buildings.

381
00:38:01,297 --> 00:38:08,403
[SPEAKER_02]: And then again, at the 607 million and same slide, same math, just a larger debt exclusion amount.

382
00:38:15,574 --> 00:38:18,696
[SPEAKER_02]: And then we looked at the seniors as part of another study that we had done.

383
00:38:18,776 --> 00:38:27,723
[SPEAKER_02]: So this just breaks down based on the registrar of voters that we got the most recent census, the number of seniors that are in Medford.

384
00:38:28,144 --> 00:38:41,454
