528
00:53:07,351 --> 00:53:23,856
[SPEAKER_15]: Okay, so safe to say, as I know some of these discussions about the comprehensive high school have been, where can we find and put these programs in other spaces, and knowing that the Hegner building is one of our few kind of vacant spaces in the city that is even potentially available, it's helpful to know that all the space in there is already spoken for, so thank you.

