02:24:37,581 --> 02:24:41,345
[SPEAKER_04]: And so all the other options kind of fall in between those.

1372
02:24:44,019 --> 02:24:48,885
[SPEAKER_04]: For the HVAC system, we selected the ground source heat pump system.

1373
02:24:48,925 --> 02:24:55,373
[SPEAKER_04]: That was one of the preferred systems that came through all the discussions during PDP and early PSR.

1374
02:24:56,013 --> 02:25:01,180
[SPEAKER_04]: And the second system we're analyzing here is air to water heat pump.

1375
02:25:01,680 --> 02:25:08,183
